OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775170980
OL,3,CGardai submit supplementary
OL,4,Cprosecution file on Creeslough
OL,5,Cexplosion
OL,7,FGardai have submitted a supplementary
OL,8,Ffile to the Office of the Director of
OL,9,FPublic Prosecutions on the Creeslough
OL,10,Fexplosion investigation.
OL,12,FTen people were killed in an explosion
OL,13,Fat a building complex in the Co
OL,14,FDonegal village on October 7 2022.
OL,16,FThe supplementary file has been
OL,17,Fsubmitted several months after the
OL,18,Fprimary file was submitted to the
OL,19,FOffice of the DPP in September 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
