OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775170980
OL,3,CGardai submit supplementary
OL,4,Cprosecution file on Creeslough
OL,5,Cexplosion
OL,7,FA Garda spokesperson said it includes
OL,8,Fformal recommendations from An Garda
OL,9,FSiochana.
OL,11,FThey said the victims' families
OL,12,Fcontinue to be supported by family
OL,13,Fliaison officers and attend regular
OL,14,Ffamily liaison briefings, the most
OL,15,Frecent of which took place on Thursday
OL,16,Fevening.
